---
title: Jalapeño Cornbread Pie with Pork and Collard Greens
description: Collard greens and cornbread are staples in American South cuisine. We've combined both to make a cornbread pie (and we've spiked it with jalapeño for some oomph!) Cornbread layered over a skillet of juicy pork, collards, and corn kernels? You’ll be licking this pan clean!
